metadata.name: The Gateway Experience #1
metadata.description: Resonance phenomena are when someone is able to connect with “greater energies and energy systems” beyond their “physical matter”. This can be done through the use of audio tones (“binaural beats”) to synchronize the energies of the left and right brain hemispheres. The aim of The Gateway Experience program is to give an introduction to these concepts and to teach the audience to be able to use these effects consciously without any aid.
